            the obj-&gt;refcount reaches 0. From there it calls
            dev-&gt;driver-&gt;gem_free_object_unlocked, which is
            amdgpu_gem_object_free in amdgpu.<br>
          </p>
          <p>Regards,<br>
            &nbsp; Felix<br>
          </p>
